Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:18.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ryu's brother that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:25.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to spend some money on him this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:34.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she gave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:42.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:45.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you. It's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:48.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back again for New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:56.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi never showed up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:01.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's busy. She's growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:03.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:07.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tell Chi to say hi properly next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:13.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:21.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:48.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a face to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:41.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother said to say hi properly next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went home around noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:52.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:55.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to be nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you starting a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:58.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:05.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You thought it'd be bad to tell me about Tohru, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't being nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:17.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it's finally come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:27.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can finally give up on my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:39.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You baseball nut!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:44.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's baseball got to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:17.75,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:22.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan does so much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:32.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if I were like Kazehaya-kun,\N I might have been able to cheer her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:57.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Chizu went to see Ryu's brother after what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:01.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she congratulated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a speck of disappointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, good going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:12.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In jeans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:21.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I know, Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:27.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should just snap for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:29.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:35.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I sort of said something to make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more fish in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:45.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did. I totally did!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu froze up for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:50.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane-chan, what did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:01.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:06.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like it bothers me when I'm hurting her deliberately, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:08.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:13.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder; what were we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:17.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were savoring our powerlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:21.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something about Yoshida?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:29.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew that was bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:33.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know who she liked too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:39.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to hang out at Ryu's a lot when Tohru was back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:42.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu's easy to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:46.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane-chan was just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:51.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She was worried about Chizu-chan, but she couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:08:02.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I can't even tell whether she's playing tough or if she's so shocked that she's in denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's supposed to be easy to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:11.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan looked happy, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:16.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what she's feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:20.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know she's not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miniskirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:28.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! We're so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:37.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! She's your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I hate guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:44.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:49.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, because she has you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can say to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:01.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I don't think that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:11.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be glad to have friends who worry for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:16.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need to force yourself to say something to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:24.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might not be able to say anything right now either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:32.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:37.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Joe just get rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:48.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should head to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:56.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering how Kazehaya-kun would help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:58.99,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:02.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really say anything to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:11.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but even so I hope there's something I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:18.13,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:26.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got comforted by a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can't really tease him as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:41.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She has Kuronuma, Yano and Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:57.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sawako and Yano-chin aren't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:14.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it's finally come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:27.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin, Sawako, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:35.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't meet up the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:38.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I even kicked you guys out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, we see each other every day anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:49.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to our seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin will be here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:55.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:12:00.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't cry; Chizu-chan's not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:17.41,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear her out if she talks to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:21.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And let her vent as much as she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:36.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to act normal around Chizu-chan until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:42.67,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's the best I can do for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:46.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:49.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, what are you having?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:51.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cafeteria food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:53.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:55.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:06.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go buy bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:08.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'll be back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:42.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Ryu talked to Chizu at all today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:50.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Ryu go after Chizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:52.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:01.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half and half, an Elizabeth with cheese and mayo,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:05.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a bagel, a melon bun, nuts and a dried fruit bun, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huge catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:35.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:39.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, you wouldn't even look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:41.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? All that stuff yesterday, and now my bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:47.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:52.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care to apologize for what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:05.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you always thinking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:12.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I was hopelessly in love with Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I should hurry up and give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:21.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:29.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't fall in love with Tohru just for the sake of getting rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:36.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really go to see Tohru yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:44.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“You're late?”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:54.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have wanted to see him properly if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:00.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:01.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:06.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I went to give you the present after he'd already have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:16.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumb shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:22.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru, your bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:26.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I eat all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:43.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't fall in love with Tohru just for the sake of getting rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:02.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:11.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sort of worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:16.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:24.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bit of a fight with Ryu yesterday night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:33.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:36.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:37.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:47.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu?! A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:56.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I gave him the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:18:01.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“I'm glad it came to this.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:06.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Now you can give up.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:08.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:11.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean it's hopeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:15.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too blunt, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:17.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:23.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you even feel sorry for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:27.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:35.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I hate myself the most for blaming him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:43.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be happier when I gave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so eager to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I threw it at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:49.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:19:00.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even understand marriage, and here I am taking it out on people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:06.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:19.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, come on, let it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:24.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When else are you going to vent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:29.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have every right to take it out on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:31.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu's totally being an asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:36.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is, right? He's a douchebag right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:38.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:41.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't even have given him the present if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:46.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:55.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin, Sawako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:57.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:58.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:01.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:06.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to his house, and he goes, “forget about him.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:10.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I give him that bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:13.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:22.05,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find any words to help Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:28.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But on the way home, she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:37.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt a bit better after you made me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:45.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go eat cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:49.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:51.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I get fat when I hang out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:04.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:10.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a ton of bread. Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:14.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:33.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shimmering night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:36.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile like you used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:39.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: First Snow
